description: Integrated Water Resource Management for Uzbekistan

subproject.description: To achieve its output, the project will perform the following activities: i) Improved Legal and Institutional Framework for Integrated Water Resources Management in Uzbekistan; ii) Improved Water Communal Services and Utilities within the Zarafshan River Basin of Uzbekistan; iii) Integrated Water Resources Management and Water Use Efficiency Plan for the Zarafshan River Basin of Uzbekistan.
